HEADWORD: Figwort
<hw>Fig"wort`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A
genus of herbaceous plants (<gen>Scrophularia</gen>), mostly found in
the north temperate zones. See <er>Brownwort</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
